open-hackathon-ui Cookbook
==================

This cookbook auto-deploys open-hackathon-tempUI.

Requirements
------------

#### packages
- `apt` - open-hackathon-ui needs apt.
- `python` - open-hackathon-ui needs python.
- `git` - open-hackathon-ui needs git.
- `uwsgi` - open-hackathon-ui needs uwsgi.
- `gcc` - gcc.

Attributes
----------

#### open-hackathon-tempUI::default
<table>
  <tr>
    <th>Key</th>
    <th>Type</th>
    <th>Description</th>
    <th>Default</th>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td><tt>['open-hackathon-ui']['HOSTNAME']</tt></td>
    <td>String</td>
    <td>the hostname of open-hackathon-ui server</td>
    <td><tt>http://open-hackathon-dev.chinacloudapp.cn</tt></td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td><tt>['open-hackathon-ui']['hackathon']['name']</tt></td>
    <td>String</td>
    <td>the name of open-hackathon-ui-dev</td>
    <td><tt>open-xml-sdk</tt></td>
  </tr>
</table>

Usage
-----
#### open-hackathon-ui::default

Just include `open-hackathon-ui` in your node's `run_list`:

```json
{
  "name":"my_node",
  "run_list": [
    "recipe[open-hackathon-ui]"
  ]
}
```

